<grammar>
<section>
<title>&lt;i&gt; this/these&lt;/i&gt; </title>
<sectiontitle> We use &lt;i&gt;this&lt;/i&gt; for an object close to us.</sectiontitle>
<titlesound>sta_gram3_3_1.mp3</titlesound>
<text1> </text1>
<text1a>&lt;b&gt;This&lt;/b&gt; building.</text1a>
<sound1>sta_gram3_3_2.mp3</sound1>
<sectiontitle2> In the plural, we use &lt;i&gt;these.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt; &lt;/i&gt;</sectiontitle2>
<titlesound2>sta_gram3_3_3.mp3</titlesound2>
<text3> </text3>
<text3a>&lt;b&gt;These&lt;/b&gt; buildings.</text3a>
<sound3>sta_gram3_3_4.mp3</sound3>
</section>
<section>
<title>&lt;i&gt;that/those&lt;/i&gt;</title>
<sectiontitle> We use &lt;i&gt;that&lt;/i&gt; for an object which isn't close to us.</sectiontitle>
<titlesound>sta_gram3_3_5.mp3</titlesound>
<text1> </text1>
<text1a>&lt;b&gt;That&lt;/b&gt; man.</text1a>
<sound1>sta_gram3_3_6.mp3</sound1>
